                            <comment id="17041642" author="jark" created="Fri, 21 Feb 2020 07:51:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=victor-wong&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;victor-wong&quot;&gt;victor-wong&lt;/a&gt;, I re-think about this issue. I think we shouldn&apos;t force to use thread context classloader, otherwise we can&apos;t support dynamic classloader in the future.  A better solution might be expose classloader to &lt;tt&gt;TableFactory#Context&lt;/tt&gt; which will be supported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-15912&quot; title=&quot;�Add Context to improve TableSourceFactory and TableSinkFactory&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-15912&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-15912&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

